summary: Trying something new.... hope you enjoy 💜💜💜 | check instagram for other bts related posts |  You and Suga have been dating now...
body:
Trying something new…. hope you enjoy 💜💜💜 | check instagram for other bts related posts | You and Suga have been dating now for 6 months and still neither one of you has said “i love you”. You were scared that he won’t say it back and vice versa.

There were moments that you would almost accidentally say i love you just because he had done something nice for you, like ordering food or even giving a simple back hug, but you somehow managed not to.

One night you suggested on going for a walk since you didn’t know what to do and he happily agreed even though he is a person that prefers to stay at home, but the reason he had no problem going out was that it was with you.

You were walking in the park, enjoying your time together, talking about different topics. Your hands were cutely tangled together and you being the kid you are, you swinged them for a solid 10 minutes and he didn’t have any problem at all, he loved that side of you.

Continuing you walk he spotted a open ice-cream shop and asked you if you would like to have some and before you had time to answer he dragged you to the store. While choosing what to order between all the different flavours, Suga noticed the boy working there checking you out from head to toe and of course you precious boyfriend got jealous, leading to hugging you from behind, leaning his head on you shoulder and being all clingy asking you loud and clear, so the male worker could hear, “What will you order, baby?”. You didn’t question his sudden actions, answering to him with the two favours that you loved the most.

When you both chose what to have you went to pay for the ice-creams, this time Suga holding your hand. Suga insisted on paying and so he could do that he had to let go of you hand. The worker initiated a conversation with you, being all flirty even though your boyfriend was right next to, paying the bill and minutes earlier holding your hand and hugging you.

Suga got so frustrated and gave him the money angrily taking the cups of ice-cream in his one hand and with his other hand taking yours again and dragging you out. You went to sit on a bench where there weren’t many people around.

He was silent which confused you, minutes earlier before you entered the shop you were talking and laughing but now you weren’t. You turned next to him noticing a small pout forming and also his ears getting a bit red. Seeing that you came to the realisation that he might have got jealous because of that boy who served you. Finding his reaction cute you started to poke his cheeks and asking him what happened and why he wasn’t talking in a sad baby voice. His pout formed even bigger making you UwU inside. That gave you an idea, since he hasn’t answering you, to start teasing him about the boy. Leading to getting him a bit angry making him confess the reason of his actions in a quiet and sad tone. Finding that even cuter you threw yourself, embracing him in a big hug, starting to kissing him again and again. “You are too cute when you are jealous!!! You know that other boys don’t impress me. I love you too much to even think about others in that way…” Not thinking before you speak, those three words slipped out of your mouth making you freeze in the position you were, in which you still hugged him. He firstly couldn’t process what you told him, it got him in surprise. Seconds later he pulled you, gave you a kiss and hugged you back tighter than ever, whispering to you: “ I love you too…”. Leaving both of you a blushing mess.
